import React from 'react' import "./login.css"; const Register = () => { const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const data = new FormData(e.currentTarget); const actualData = { name:data.get('name') , email: data.get('email'), password: data.get('password'), password_confirmation:data.get('password_confirmation') } return <>
Name
Email
Password
Confirm Password
; }} export default Register
